<div class="row">
    <div class="column-3">

        <h2>Create</h2>
        <p>
            Create pages for your characters and stories to keep track of. Create pages characters that you've had for a couple years or a character
            that you thought of while half asleep.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="column-3">

        <h2>develop</h2>
        <p>
            Further develop your characters in your stories and turn them into interesting 3-demensional characters that'll
            make your stories amazing.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="column-3">

        <h2>convenience</h2>
        <p>
            Have all your characters, story outlines, snippets, and world building in one place for your convenience as a writer.

        </p>
    </div>
</div>

